Package org.apache.shale.tiger.managed.rules

Digester rules (and ManagedBeansRuleSet) for parsing managed bean elements from a faces-config.xml resource.

          Description

Class Summary
ListEntriesRule Digester rule for processing a <list-entries> element.
ListEntryRule Digester rule for processing a <list-entries> nested element.
ManagedBeanRule Digester rule for processing a <managed-bean> element.
ManagedBeansRuleSet Digester RuleSet for parsing managed bean declarations from a JavaServer Faces configuration file.
ManagedPropertyRule Digester rule for processing a <managed-property> element.
MapEntriesRule Digester rule for processing a <map-entries> element.
MapEntryRule Digester rule for processing a <map-entry> element.
NullValueRule Digester rule for processing a <null-value> element.
